Geometry optimisation options
\begin_inset LatexCommand \label{Sec::Geometry-optimisation-options}

\end_inset 


\layout Subsubsection*
\noindent 
max_opt
\layout Standard
\noindent 
Maximum number of relaxation iterations (N) to be used within the optimisation
 method chosen (see below).
 
\layout Standard
\noindent 

\emph on 
Options
\emph default 
: N
\layout Standard
\noindent 

\emph on 
Default
\emph default 
: N =
\series bold 
 100
\layout Standard
\noindent 

\emph on 
Example
\emph default 
: 
\series bold 
